  <entry>
    <title>张宇1000题第一章强化训练(二)</title>
    <url>/2022/04/25/%E5%BC%A0%E5%AE%871000%E9%A2%98%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E7%AB%A0%E5%BC%BA%E5%8C%96%E8%AE%AD%E7%BB%83-%E4%BA%8C/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="\assets\css\APlayer.min.css"><script src="\assets\js\APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><script class="meting-secondary-script-marker" src="\assets\js\Meting.min.js"></script><ol start="23" type="1">
<li><span class="math display">\[
\lim_{x-&gt;0}{\frac{\int_{sinx}^{x}{\sqrt{3+t^2}dt}}{x(e^{x^2}-1)}}=\lim_{x-&gt;0}{\frac{(x-sinx)\sqrt{3+\xi^2}}{x*x^2}}=\lim_{x-&gt;0}{\frac{[x-x+\frac{1}{6}x^3+o(x^3)]\sqrt{3+\xi^2}}{x^3}}=\frac{\sqrt{3+\xi^2}}{6}
\]</span></li>
</ol>
<p><span class="math display">\[
(\xi介于sinx与x之间)，x-&gt;0,有夹逼准则可知\xi-&gt;0
\]</span></p>
<p><span class="math display">\[
原式=\frac{\sqrt{3}}{6}
\]</span></p>
<p><span class="math display">\[
本题用到了积分中值定理，\int_{a}^{b}{f(x)}dx=f(\xi)(b-a)
\]</span></p>
<span id="more"></span>
<ol start="26" type="1">
<li></li>
</ol>
<p>（5） <span class="math display">\[
\lim_{x-&gt;\infty}{e^{-x}(1+\frac{1}{x})^{x^2}}=\lim_{x-&gt;\infty}{e^{-x}*e^{x^2ln(1+\frac{1}{x})}}=\lim_{x-&gt;\infty}{e^{x^2*ln(1+\frac{1}{x})-x}}=\lim_{x-&gt;\infty}{e^{x^2[ln(1+\frac{1}{x})-\frac{1}{x}]}}=\lim_{x-&gt;\infty}{e^{x^2(\frac{1}{x}-\frac{1}{2x^2}+o(x^2)-\frac{1}{x})}}=e^{-\frac{1}{2}}
\]</span> 本题不可用第二个重要极限 <span class="math display">\[
\lim_{x-&gt;\infty}{(1+\frac{1}{x})^x}=e
\]</span></p>
<p><span class="math display">\[
如果将原式中x^2换成x，则可以使用上式，本题我们使用1^\infty做题，将(1+\frac{1}{x})^{x^2}(幂指函数)写成e^{x^2ln(1+\frac{1}{x})},结合泰勒公式可以求解
\]</span></p>
<p>（7） <span class="math display">\[
\lim_{x-&gt;\infty}{x^2(a^{\frac{1}{x}}+a^{-\frac{1}{x}}-2)},a&gt;0,a\ne1;
\]</span></p>
<p><span class="math display">\[
\lim_{x-&gt;\infty}{\frac{a^{\frac{1}{x}}+a^{-\frac{1}{x}}-2}{\frac{1}{x^2}}}=\lim_{t-&gt;0}{\frac{a^{t}+a^{-t}-2}{t^2}}=\lim_{t-&gt;0}{\frac{lna*a^t-lna*a^{-t}}{2t}}=\lim_{t-&gt;0}{\frac{ln^2a*a^t+ln^2a*a^{-t}}{2}}=ln^2a
\]</span></p>
<p>（19） <span class="math display">\[
\lim_{x-&gt;0^+}{\frac{x^x-(tanx)^x}{x(\sqrt{1+3sin^2x}-1)}}=\frac{2}{3}\lim_{x-&gt;0^+}{\frac{x^x(1-(\frac{tanx}{x})^x)}{x^3}}=-\frac{2}{3}\lim_{x-&gt;0^+}{\frac{x^x[x(\frac{tanx}{x}-1)]}{x^3}}=-\frac{2}{3}\lim_{x-&gt;0^+}{\frac{tanx-x}{x^3}}=-\frac{2}{9}
\]</span></p>
]]></content>
