    <title>汤家凤1800第一章极限函数连续</title>
    <url>/2022/05/03/%E6%B1%A4%E5%AE%B6%E5%87%A41800%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E7%AB%A0%E6%9E%81%E9%99%90%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%E8%BF%9E%E7%BB%AD/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="\assets\css\APlayer.min.css"><script src="\assets\js\APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><script class="meting-secondary-script-marker" src="\assets\js\Meting.min.js"></script><iframe src="//player.bilibili.com/player.html?aid=765351757&amp;bvid=BV1yr4y1m7sg&amp;cid=475213100&amp;page=1" scrolling="no" border="0" frameborder="no" framespacing="0" allowfullscreen="true">
</iframe>
<span id="more"></span>
<ol type="1">
<li><p><span class="math display">\[
\lim_{x-&gt;0}{\frac{tanx-sinx}{x^2ln(1+2x)}}=\lim_{x-&gt;0}{\frac{tanx-sinx}{2x^3}}=\lim_{x-&gt;0}{\frac{tanx(1-cosx)}{2x^3}}=\lim_{x-&gt;0}{\frac{x*\frac{1}{2}x^2}{2x^3}}\\=\frac{1}{4}
\]</span> 也可以使用泰勒公式 <span class="math display">\[
\lim_{x-&gt;0}{\frac{tanx-sinx}{x^2ln(1+2x)}}=\lim_{x-&gt;0}{\frac{x+\frac{1}{3}x^3+o(x^3)-x+\frac{1}{6}x^3+o(x^3)}{2x^3}}=\frac{1}{4}
\]</span> <br></p></li>
<li><p><span class="math display">\[
\lim_{x-&gt;\infty}{(\frac{x}{1+x})^{2x}}=\lim_{x-&gt;\infty}{(1-\frac{1}{1+x})^{-(1+x)*-\frac{1}{1+x}*2x}}=\lim_{x-&gt;\infty}{e^{-\frac{2x}{1+x}}}=e^{-2}
\]</span> <br></p></li>
<li><p><span class="math display">\[
\lim_{x-&gt;\infty}{\frac{2x^2+xcosx+1}{x^2+xsin\frac{2}{x}}}=\lim_{x-&gt;\infty}{\frac{2+\frac{cosx}{x}+\frac{1}{x^2}}{1+\frac{sin\frac{2}{x}}{x}}}=2
\]</span> 此题不要使用洛必达法则，而是分子分母同时除以x^2</p></li>
</ol>
<p><br></p>
<ol start="4" type="1">
<li><span class="math display">\[
\lim_{x-&gt;\infty}{\frac{ln(3x^2+2x+2)}{ln(2x^4+3x-1)}}=\lim_{x-&gt;\infty}{\frac{\frac{6x+2}{3x^2+2x+2}}{\frac{8x^3+3}{2x^4+3x-1}}}=\lim_{x-&gt;\infty}{\frac{(6x+2)(2x^4+3x-1)}{(8x^3+3)(3x^2+2x+2)}}=\frac{1}{2}
\]</span> 使用洛必达法则除以lnx函数，再使用抓大头的方式求解</li>
</ol>
<p><br></p>
<ol start="5" type="1">
<li><p><span class="math display">\[
\lim_{x-&gt;0}{(\frac{1}{1-cosx}-\frac{2}{x^2})}=\lim_{x-&gt;0}{\frac{x^2-2(1-cosx)}{x^2(1-cosx)}}=\lim_{x-&gt;0}{\frac{x^2+2cosx-2}{x^2*\frac{1}{2}x^2}}=\lim_{x-&gt;0}{\frac{2x-2sinx}{2x^3}}=\lim_{x-&gt;0}{\frac{2(1-cosx)}{6x^2}}=\lim_{x-&gt;0}{\frac{x^2}{6x^2}}=\frac{1}{6}
\]</span> <br></p></li>
<li><p><span class="math display">\[
\lim_{x-&gt;+\infty}{(\sqrt{x^2+4x+1}-\sqrt{x^2-2x+2})}=\lim_{x-&gt;+\infty}{\frac{6x-1}{\sqrt{x^2+4x+1}+\sqrt{x^2-2x+2}}}=\lim_{x-&gt;+\infty}{\frac{6x}{2x}}=3
\]</span> <br></p></li>
<li><p><span class="math display">\[
当x-&gt;0时，\sqrt{1+ax^2}-1\sim1-cos^2x,则a=\\
\]</span> <span class="math display">\[
\lim_{x-&gt;0}{\frac{\sqrt{1+ax^2}-1}{1-cos^2x}}=\lim_{x-&gt;0}{\frac{\frac{1}{2}ax^2}{x^2}}=\frac{1}{2}a=1,a=2\\
\]</span></p></li>
</ol>
<p><span class="math display">\[
或者1-cos^2x\sim\frac{2}{2}x^2,根据1-cos^nnx\sim\frac{n}{2}(nx)^2
\]</span></p>
<p><br></p>
<ol start="8" type="1">
<li><span class="math display">\[
设\lim_{x-&gt;\infty}{(\frac{x+c}{x-c})^{\frac{2x^2+3x+2}{x+1}}}=\lim_{x-&gt;0}{(cosx+x^2)^{\frac{1}{sin^2x}}}\\
\]</span></li>
</ol>
<p><span class="math display">\[
\lim_{x-&gt;\infty}{(\frac{x-c+2c}{x-c})^{\frac{2x^2+3x+2}{x+1}}}=\lim_{x-&gt;\infty}{(1+\frac{2c}{x-c})^{\frac{x-c}{2c}*\frac{2c}{x-c}*\frac{2x^2+3x+2}{x+1}}}=\lim_{x-&gt;\infty}{e^{\frac{2c}{x-c}*\frac{2x^2+3x+2}{x+1}}}=e^{4c}\\
\]</span></p>
<p><span class="math display">\[
\lim_{x-&gt;0}{(1+cosx+x^2-1)^{\frac{1}{cosx+x^2-1}*(cosx+x^2-1)*\frac{1}{sin^2x}}}=\lim_{x-&gt;0}{e^{\frac{cosx+x^2-1}{sin^2x}}}=\lim_{x-&gt;0}{e^{\frac{\frac{1}{2}x^2}{x^2}}}=e^{\frac{1}{2}}\\
\]</span></p>
<p><span class="math display">\[
e^{4c}=e^{\frac{1}{2}},c=\frac{1}{8}
\]</span></p>
<p><br></p>
<ol start="9" type="1">
<li><span class="math display">\[
\begin{equation}
f(x)=\left\{
  \begin{aligned}
  \frac{arctan3x+e^{ax}-1}{x} \quad x&lt;0\\
  1 \quad x=0\\
  \frac{1-(1-x^2)^b}{xarcsin2x} \quad x&gt;0\\
  \end{aligned}
  \right
  .
\end{equation}\\
f(x)在x=0处连续，则a=,b=
\]</span></li>
</ol>
<p><span class="math display">\[
\lim_{x-&gt;0^-}{\frac{arctan3x+e^{ax}-1}{x}}=\lim_{x-&gt;0^-}{\frac{\frac{3}{1+9x^2}+ae^{ax}}{1}}=3+a\\
\]</span></p>
<p><span class="math display">\[
\lim_{x-&gt;0^+}{\frac{1-(1-x^2)^b}{xarcsin2x}}=\lim_{x-&gt;0^+}{\frac{-(-bx^2)}{2x^2}}=\frac{b}{2}\\
\]</span></p>
<p><span class="math display">\[
f(x)在x=0处连续,f(0^+)=f(0^-)=f(0)=1\\
\]</span></p>
<p><span class="math display">\[
a=-2  
\]</span></p>
<p><span class="math display">\[
b=2
\]</span></p>
<p><br></p>
<ol start="10" type="1">
<li><span class="math display">\[
f(x)=\frac{2-e^{\frac{1}{x}}}{1+e^{\frac{1}{x}}}*arctan\frac{1}{x}\\
\]</span></li>
</ol>
<p><span class="math display">\[
x=0为f(x)的?间断点\\
\]</span></p>
<p><span class="math display">\[
\lim_{x-&gt;0^+}{f(x)}=\frac{\pi}{2}\lim_{x-&gt;0^+}{\frac{\frac{e^{\frac{1}{x}}}{x^2}}{-\frac{e^{\frac{1}{x}}}{x^2}}}=-\frac{\pi}{2}\\
\]</span></p>
<p><span class="math display">\[
\lim_{x-&gt;0^-}{f(x)}=-\frac{\pi}{2}\lim_{x-&gt;0^-}{\frac{2}{1}}=-\pi
\]</span></p>
<p><span class="math display">\[
f(0^-),f(0^+)都存在，但不相等，所以x=0是f(x)的跳跃间断点，属于第一类间断点
\]</span></p>
<p><br></p>
<ol type="1">
<li><span class="math display">\[
\lim_{x-&gt;0}{\frac{x-sinax}{\int_{0}^{x}{\frac{t^2}{\sqrt{b+t^4}}dt}}}=2
